-- Lebanese Minister Survives Attack on His Convoy, NNA Says
-- B y   D o n n a   A b u - N a s r
-- 2013-01-18T12:50:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-18/lebanese-minister-survives-attack-on-his-convoy-nna-says.html
The convoy of Lebanese Minister of
Youth and Sports Faysal Karami came under fire in the northern
city of Tripoli today and four of his bodyguards were injured,
the official National News Agency said.  Karami survived the attack and the army has deployed troops
near his residence, the agency said. The city has seen
intermittent clashes between supporters and opponents of Syrian
President Bashar al-Assad.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Donna Abu-Nasr in Dubai at 
 dabunasr@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
